 SERVICES :
     
            * systemctl stop sshd.service (to stop)
            * systemctl start sshd.service 
            * systemctl restart sshd.service 
            * systemctl reload sshd.service (instead of restart)[applicable to some]
            * systemctl status sshd.service (show details)
            * systemctl reload-or-restart sshd.service 
            * systemctl disable sshd.service 
            * systemctl is-enabled sshd.service (to check enable)
            * systemctl enable sshd.service 
            * systemctl enable --now sshd.service (to start now itself)
            * systemctl mask sshd.service (not to enable or start again)
            * systemctl unmask sshd.service 
            * systemctl list-units --type service --all (to view all services status) .
          
